## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not provide the most up-to-date data or comprehensive analysis. Additionally, the feasibility of a 100% renewable energy system is contingent on various factors, including political will, economic investment, and technological breakthroughs, which are subject to change. Furthermore, the environmental and social impacts of transitioning to renewable energy were not extensively covered in the available sources.

